  "prompt": "What are some good Hindi songs (female) for an audition?",
  "response": "If you're preparing for an audition and looking for Hindi songs that showcase your vocal range, expression, and versatility, here are some excellent **female-led** Hindi songs to consider. These songs span different genres, moods, and vocal techniques:\n\n### **Classic/Evergreen Songs**\n1. **\"Lag Jaa Gale\"** - Lata Mangeshkar (Classic, soulful)  \n2. **\"Piya Tose Naina Lage Re\"** - Lata Mangeshkar (Romantic, classical)  \n3. **\"Aaj Jaane Ki Zid Na Karo\"** - Farida Khanum (Ghazal, emotional)  \n4. **\"Inhi Logon Ne\"** - Lata Mangeshkar (Ghazal, intense)  \n5. **\"Bole Re Papi Hara\"** - Lata Mangeshkar (Folk, vibrant)\n\n### **Semi-Classical/Sufi Songs**\n1. **\"Kun Faya Kun\"** - Shreya Ghoshal (Sufi, spiritual)  \n2. **\"Mohe Rang Do Laal\"** - Shreya Ghoshal (Semi-classical, vibrant)  \n3. **\"Jag Ghoomeya\"** - Neha Bhasin (Sufi, energetic)  \n4. **\"Chaap Tilak\"** - Shreya Ghoshal (Qawwali, soulful)  \n5. **\"O Re Piya\"** - Rahat Fateh Ali Khan & Alka Yagnik (Sufi, emotional)\n\n### **Upbeat/Pop Songs**\n1. **\"Nagada Sang Dhol\"** - Shreya Ghoshal & Osman Mir (Energetic, festive)  \n2. **\"Kala Chashma\"** - Neha Kakkar, Badshah (Peppy, party vibe)  \n3. **\"London Thumakda\"** - Shreya Ghoshal (Fun, energetic)  \n4. **\"Kamli\"** - Harshdeep Kaur (Folk, vibrant)  \n5. **\"Sheila Ki Jawani\"** - Sunidhi Chauhan (Bold, peppy)\n\n### **Emotional/Ballad Songs**\n1. **\"Tum Hi Ho\"** - Shreya Ghoshal (Soft, romantic)  \n2. **\"Samjhawan\"** - Shreya Ghoshal & Arijit Singh (Emotional, romantic)  \n3. **\"Teri Umeed Tera Intezar\"** - Lata Mangeshkar (Ghazal, heartwarming)  \n4. **\"Hasi\"** - Shreya Ghoshal (Sweet, romantic)  \n5. **\"Phir Le Aaya Dil\"** - Rekha Bhardwaj & Arijit Singh (Emotional, soulful)\n\n### **High-Energy/Rock/Powerful Songs**\n1. **\"Barso Re\"** - Shreya Ghoshal (Energetic, classic)  \n2. **\"Ziddi Dil\"** - Neeti Mohan (Rock, powerful)  \n3. **\"Chikni Chameli\"** - Shreya Ghoshal (Bold, energetic)  \n4. **\"Galliyan\"** - Ankit Tiwari & Neeti Mohan (Emotional yet powerful)  \n5. **\"Pinga\"** - Shreya Ghoshal & Vaishali Mhade (Energetic, classical)\n\n### **Contemporary/Latest Hits**\n1. **\"Leja Re\"** - Dhvani Bhanushali (Romantic, modern)  \n2. **\"Raatan Lambiyan\"** - Jubin Nautiyal, Asees Kaur (Soft, romantic)  \n3. **\"Garmi\"** - Neha Kakkar & Badshah (Energetic, peppy)  \n4. **\"Dilbar\"** - Neha Kakkar (Energetic, modern)  \n5. **\"Kya Karoon?\"** - Clinton Cerejo & Nikhil D'Souza (Unique, modern)\n\n### Tips for Auditions:\n- Choose a song that suits your **vocal range** and **style**.  \n- Pick a song that allows you to **emote** and **connect** with the audience.  \n- Practice **breath control** and **enunciation** for clarity.  \n- Avoid overly complicated songs if you're not confident with their technical aspects.  \n- Add your **unique touch** to make the performance memorable.\n\nGood luck with your audition! \ud83c\udf1f \ud83c\udfa4",
